When Cursor auto-generates a Git commit message (Source Control ✨), output MUST strictly follow Angular Conventional Commits. Subject and body in Simplified Chinese; type and scope in English lowercase.

CRITICAL — first line MUST match this pattern exactly:
<type>(<scope>): <subject>
or (when no scope):
<type>: <subject>

Valid types: feat | fix | docs | style | refactor | perf | test | build | ci | chore | revert

FORBIDDEN first lines (never output these):
❌ 新增中文约定式提交规则与 VSCode 设置文件
❌ Add commit rules and VSCode settings
❌ 任何不以 type: 或 type(scope): 开头的句子

REQUIRED structure:
Line 1: <type>(<scope>): <中文 subject>   ← mandatory prefix, never skip
Line 2: empty line
Line 3+: bullet list body (optional)

Rules:
- subject: Simplified Chinese, ≤50 chars, imperative, no period at end
- body: Simplified Chinese bullets starting with "- "
- scope examples: cursor, todo, vscode, api — omit parentheses only if truly no module

Type guide for this repo:
- .cursorrules / .cursor/rules → chore(cursor)
- .vscode/settings.json → chore(vscode) or include in chore(cursor)
- new app feature → feat(<module>)
- bug fix → fix(<module>)
- README only → docs

Correct example for rule + settings changes:
chore(cursor): 新增中文约定式提交规则与 VSCode 设置

- 新增 .cursorrules 定义 SCM 提交格式
- 新增 conventional-commits-zh.mdc 供 Agent 使用
- 新增 .vscode/settings.json 配置 Python 环境

Other examples:
feat(todo): 添加任务筛选与批量清除功能
fix(todo): 修复重复任务无法删除的问题
docs: 补充 Todo List 本地运行说明
